{"ec":"ET00000847","t":"Ram Lakhan (1989)","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/ram-lakhan-et00000847-23-09-2016-06-50-01.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/ram-lakhan-et00000847-23-09-2016-06-50-01.jpg","d":"Sharda is enraged and eyes vengeance when her husband is murdered by his two cousins, Bhishamber and Bhanu causing her and her two young sons to be thrown out of their house. One of her sons, Ram grows up to be a policeman, while her second son, Lakhan turns out to be a rather ignoble man. If the family wants to stand by their vow of vengeance, Ram will have to compel his brother to mend his ways, and stay away from Bhanu and Bhishamber.","rd":"1989-07-27","rt":174,"ct":"U","g":["Action","Drama"],"l":["Hindi","Bengali"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Jackie Shroff","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/jackie-shroff-882-19-09-2017-05-13-08.jpg"],["Anil Kapoor","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anil-kapoor-176-12-09-2017-07-42-36.jpg"],["Madhuri Dixit","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/madhuri-dixit-1318-29-09-2016-01-48-46.jpg"],["Dimple Kapadia","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/dimple-kapadia-595-19-09-2017-05-14-09.jpg"],["Rakhee Gulzar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/rakhee-gulzar-5220-24-03-2017-17-27-27.jpg"],["Amrish Puri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/amrish-puri-4574-24-03-2017-17-31-53.jpg"],["Gulshan Grover","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/gulshan-grover-773-24-03-2017-18-02-09.jpg"],["Anupam Kher","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/anupam-kher-211-09-10-2017-04-27-29.jpg"],["Paresh Rawal","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/paresh-rawal-1644-13